  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You may enhance an object to either increase or decrease its hardness, or enhance a creature to grant it or lessen its damage reduction. You may increase or decrease an object&#8217;s hardness by an amount equal to your caster level (minimum 1). Decreasing an object&#8217;s hardness gives it the fragile quality if it does not already have it. When targeting a creature, you may either grant it DR/adamantine equal to 1/2 your caster level (minimum 1), or decrease its current damage reduction by the same amount. This only affects damage reduction that can be bypassed (so it could decrease DR/cold iron, but not DR/-).</p>\n",
